Package fr.insa.rennes.info.chemical.user

Interface Summary
InertEventListener This interface describes a special EventListener which can be used to detect the inertia of a solution.
ReactionRule This interface describes a ReactionRule which can be added and react in a solution.
 

Class Summary
InertEvent This class represents a special EventObject which will be fired during the detection of a solution inertia.
 

Enum Summary
ReactionRule.Multiplicity Enumerates the different possible multiplicities for a reaction.
 

Annotation Types Summary
Dontputback This annotation exists for testing purpose only, and therefore should not be used.
Dontreact This annotation permits to indicate that the following reactive should not react during the reaction process.
Dontuse This annotation permits to indicate that the computeSelect() method will not be used in the reaction.
